thread.title: Jenny L

author: Jenny L
title: Jenny L
text: AMI Clubwear is legit. They have the hottest, sexiest, and seriously so many kinds of swimsuits tailored to women of various shapes and sizes. I love that they have so much to offer and is incredibly affordable! AMI even provides a good amount of discount codes. My friends have shopped here before and their happiness with AMI Clubwear swimsuits has driven me to purchase one as well. I love their stuff and can't wait to receive my swimsuit in the mail!
